<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0229c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0229c0101">妙<note n="0229001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣅀＝旨【史】</note><note n="0229001" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣅀【佛拓】，旨【史】</note><app n="0229001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣅀</rdg></app>幽微。非聖無以盡於源。聖行之興。非
<lb ed="I" n="0229c02" type="honorific"/>福智莊嚴。豈能弘其道。然今合邑諸人等。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c03" type="honorific"/>宿殖<note n="0229002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朙＝明【史】</note><note n="0229002" resp="ihp" type="mod">朙【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0229002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>珠。久歷諸佛。故能異心同<note n="0229003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31068"/>＝契【史】</note><note n="0229003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31068"/>【佛拓】，契【史】</note><app n="0229003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">契</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31068"/></rdg></app>。仰慕
<lb ed="I" n="0229c04" type="honorific"/>遺蹤。在於定光像<note n="0229004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31069"/>＝前【史】</note><note n="0229004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31069"/>【佛拓】，前【史】</note><app n="0229004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31069"/></rdg></app>。敬造七佛寶堪。并二
<lb ed="I" n="0229c05" type="honorific"/>菩薩。賢聖諸僧。<note n="0229005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02793"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0229005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02793"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0229005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app><note n="0229006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31171"/>＝勒【史】</note><note n="0229006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31171"/>【佛拓】，勒【史】</note><app n="0229006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31171"/></rdg></app>下生。梵王帝釋。舍利
<lb ed="I" n="0229c06" type="honorific"/>非<note n="0229007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡕄＝壹【史】</note><note n="0229007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡕄【佛拓】，壹【史】</note><app n="0229007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壹</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡕄</rdg></app>。其<note n="0229008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30645"/>＝金【史】</note><note n="0229008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30645"/>【佛拓】，金【史】</note><app n="0229008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>容赫弈。照曜三千。<note n="0229009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31070"/>＝華【史】</note><note n="0229009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31070"/>【佛拓】，華【史】</note><app n="0229009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31070"/></rdg></app>麗二相。妙
<lb ed="I" n="0229c07" type="honorific"/>菀八十。剋木圖<note n="0229010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">埿＝泥【史】</note><note n="0229010" resp="ihp" type="mod">埿【佛拓】，泥【史】</note><app n="0229010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">埿</rdg></app>。像而非喻。採壁模形。焉
<lb ed="I" n="0229c08" type="honorific"/>是其譬。睹之者淨信開<app type="star" corresp="#0229002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>。虔禮者三鄣殄
<lb ed="I" n="0229c09" type="honorific"/>息。斯乃塵勞之中。紹如來種。籍此勝<note n="0229011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧨅＝善【史】</note><note n="0229011" resp="ihp" type="mod">𧨅【佛拓】，善【史】</note><app n="0229011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧨅</rdg></app>。仰
<lb ed="I" n="0229c10" type="honorific"/>願國祚永隆。三寶增盛。法界四生。七世先
<lb ed="I" n="0229c11" type="honorific"/>靈。存<note n="0229012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">兦＝亡【史】</note><note n="0229012" resp="ihp" type="mod">兦【佛拓】，亡【史】</note><app n="0229012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">兦</rdg></app>父母。現在眷屬。發菩提心。<app type="star" corresp="#0229005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0229006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31171"/></rdg></app>下
<lb ed="I" n="0229c12" type="honorific"/>生。恒為導首。開化群迷。廣修万行。共集<app type="star" corresp="#0229011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧨅</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0229c13" type="honorific"/>根。同證菩提之道。刊銘頌曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c14" type="honorific"/>法性如如。非有非<note n="0229c1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0229c1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>。體非分別。妙用非虛。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c15" type="honorific"/>八相成道。似同凡夫。生而非生。滅而非滅。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c16" type="honorific"/>神通隱顯。摩王歸軼。化導三千。人天獨步。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c17" type="honorific"/>改迷接聖。慈悲覺<note n="0229013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡩺＝寤【史】</note><note n="0229013" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡩺【佛拓】，寤【史】</note><app n="0229013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡩺</rdg></app>。示三空門。令遊正路。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c18" type="honorific"/>淨修波若。四攝資助。奮翼道品。菩提永固。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c19" type="honorific"/>　　天統三年歲次丁亥三月壬申朔十五日丙戊建</p>
